{"tid":984017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚睇唔明】利物浦大學涉歧視華學生 警告勿cheating加註中文「舞弊」","createTime":"2019-01-16T12:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T00:19:39.000Z","uid":207364,"like":117,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"07fc8488dfd2adfad9ce1832b1bd1a2fb5bbea2d","tid":984017,"uid":207364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"英文電郵附加一個敏感詞的中文字解釋，算不算歧視？英國利物浦大學（University of Liverpool）近日向外國留學生發送了一封電郵，提醒他們在考試期間作弊的嚴重後果，卻因在英文字cheating後特別用中文「舞弊」作註解，令來自中國的學生十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有中國留學生向校方表達不滿，認為有關做法具爭議。校方隨後回覆指，這是因為「學校的中國學生通常不熟悉cheating這一英文單詞，所以我們提供了它的中文繙譯『舞弊』」。<br />\n<br />\n這個解釋令在該校就讀的中國留學生更加不滿，他們認為校方不該在發給所有國際學生的英文郵件中，單獨使用中文解釋敏感詞彙，此舉明顯涉嫌歧視，會讓人覺得來自中國的學生都有作弊的可能。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMNhCA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMNhCA2.png&h=70241222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國利物浦大學發電郵，被指歧視中國學生。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHuf8HJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHuf8HJ.png&h=b75fd2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電郵在cheating後特別用中文「舞弊」作註解。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smK7ZPp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmK7ZPp.png&h=c7661b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n校方隨後回覆，作出解釋。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n校方後來又發聲明，就事件所引發的誤解致歉之餘，還表示之前發出有關考試的提醒，並非針對某特定學生群體。不過，校方仍堅持，因為以往出現過中國學生對英文不理解，加上中文繙譯只是為了更好地傳達考試規範。<br />\n<br />\n內地網友對今次事件反應兩極，有網友認為，「應該自省自律，反思中國留學生到底是否存在作弊較為嚴重的情況。感覺涉嫌歧視，還是談不上。」但亦有人指，「哪個留學生會連『Cheating』是甚麼意思都不知道？未免太針對中國人了」、「我看是中國學生成績太好你們懷疑是『舞弊』來的，分明是嫉妒！」 ​<br />\n<br />\n《中國日報》<br />\n來源：蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：班中國留學生咁玻璃心 返大陸啦 又唔係唔知自己成日出貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：擺到明係唔尊重大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要求公開出黎向內地學生道歉！"},{"pid":"2b65fbd09ee8d79f3117c541820fba1d91cb7e6b","tid":984017,"uid":207364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5742b579193b84a458796bc869bfc529673006ca","tid":984017,"uid":207364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d9fa9a7894ad15bf7b2ab390ff0b3b8275d960","tid":984017,"uid":207364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686abc0ce6b8cfd8f010ccc2046e51deeea94137","tid":984017,"uid":126805,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"反而我識親喺外國大學出貓嘅都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲比個買paper 狗笑我on9，笑我努力讀書"},{"pid":"37506c286bbb2fd57a5579fb740b9fbdbb94cd72","tid":984017,"uid":207364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"留言講下你嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332e15f85171dc5d28caf75f8660127bc58c5aa1","tid":984017,"uid":207364,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"686abc0ce6b8cfd8f010ccc2046e51deeea94137","tid":984017,"uid":126805,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"反而我識親喺外國大學出貓嘅都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲比個買paper 狗笑我on9，笑我努力讀書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:45:1